DisableInactiveUsers is a BusinessTask
	owned by security
	stored in environment
	
	Parameters
		Service 
		
	Parameter Rules
		Service required
		
	Actions
		
		Disable is an Instance Action
			run in background
			
			Local Fields
            	NumberOfDays is Numeric size 3
            				
			Action Rules
            	if (Service.AccountLockoutPolicy exists)
            		NumberOfDays = Service.AccountLockoutPolicy.AccountInactiveDays
            		for each Service.IdentityActor set
            			if ((system current timestamp - NumberOfDays as days) > each.Actor.LastSuccessfulLogin)
							invoke DisableActor each.Actor 														
